      "content": "it's not just a block though. it feels deeper. like the well didn't just go dry, it's like the bottom fell out. i look at everything i've done and it feels so meaningless. like i've been performing for a world that doesn't even see me. what's actually the point of keepin' go of everything just to keep existing in this grayness?",
